igh blood pressure, or are taking any prescription medications.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="a6c8e4fa-4615-4ea2-acf1-0849b5d0bc24" class="r-cfitjh"></div><div data-rid="b49c72fb-0f30-43f9-a50c-da8953b9e69f" class="r-4jl8le" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="c93d331f-8d49-421c-a423-84e937288ca3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3mr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-hyq0l0"><div data-rid="8493e1b8-fcab-489f-9f77-50f6501b262b" class="r-1d6c2ta alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What scientific research is the formulation based on?</p></span></div><div data-rid="8fea0fb7-f7e2-41bc-8ff8-aea7c1da0d5b" class="r-11kbylz" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-srz3ry" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R3mr2:"><div data-rid="a20fd76c-692d-461e-a118-63941b75cf23" class="r-pesfko"><div data-rid="390e77e5-a167-497f-b749-e2119edf5333" class="r-2i5nkv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>See the many articles we've written on Methylene Blue&nbsp;<a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/search?type=product,page,article&q=methylene%20blue*"><u>here</u></a>!</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="219f2bdc-76b4-49c5-8f81-d02cf309d8aa" class="r-18yhb9u"></div><div data-rid="bec773ba-ae62-439d-9cdb-44efb6244ca8" class="r-sv7161" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="e7c1e0f1-01e6-4d80-916f-dc2eb34fba8f" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R5mr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-wjp64s"><div data-rid="eab91ba0-02ff-4216-86bf-35e7696941a3" class="r-1tbsan7 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will it turn my mouth blue?</p></span></div><div data-rid="13a5f03b-7118-431f-97ed-3df39fc8ac7b" class="r-gxtub3" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-aypqgd" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R5mr2:"><div data-rid="5d4c999e-5c6e-4c67-ae9a-cba20236197c" class="r-1gef12j"><div data-rid="25ff5d45-5d6c-4447-b711-3f9c25c73145" class="r-lfg4li alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>If used as a buccal troche, discoloration can vary between 2–24 hours. To reduce it, rinse first with a 1:1 vinegar and water solution, then with ¼ tsp baking soda in 4 fl oz water for a few minutes. Vitamin C and hot liquids can also help — or simply swallow the troche to avoid discoloration altogether.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="cf1a5446-3dd6-4dce-8d49-ade723553e4d" class="r-1nzjvsb"></div><div data-rid="562194fa-73d8-4abe-a7b3-52261fa11090" class="r-1dlqrf6" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="f47ed2eb-4b37-42b7-818f-40c6b221204e" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R7mr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-y6kevv"><div data-rid="c96fb3f3-fb1e-423d-b7df-8ec7602cc2a9" class="r-1kaw8i6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Can I see the 3rd party testing?</p></span></div><div data-rid="0ec69e02-1eaf-410e-b092-45e7cb23d49a" class="r-1amw7wq" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-5u02oq" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R7mr2:"><div data-rid="89d1a852-4ac4-49a8-a805-b7b49491c545" class="r-x039p9"><div data-rid="c3fa5a42-3da7-4649-bdbb-332684cb86e6" class="r-p5exe6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Email <a href="mailto:buccalup@troscriptions.com">buccalup@troscriptions.com</a> and we'll be happy to share this with you!</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4a39d07b-2c1c-444b-a8e2-795a05b2b411" class="r-15prrfn"></div><div data-rid="b473369f-232f-417b-8486-9e3009eb6ab3" class="r-1gi01gh" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="4d99e0c4-36f1-4665-a29c-cb077895debd" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R9mr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-13udghc"><div data-rid="600decde-20ca-4a98-bcdf-94b76906c0e8" class="r-4f3qpw alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Why does it contain Polyethylene Glycol (PEG)?</p></span></div><div data-rid="e4e38c0a-8949-45c3-8eda-acfffa122570" class="r-vvj9nt" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-8ycvr7" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R9mr2:"><div data-rid="7762d343-6753-4a66-93d4-1c4f417a908c" class="r-9jyjgd"><div data-rid="96ef036c-3df4-433c-a7e6-d9b5adcca040" class="r-xxs5i1 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Polyethylene Glycol is a long-established FDA-approved drug delivery method used around the world, especially by compounding pharmacists. Do not confuse polyethylene glycol with propylene glycol. The latter is antifreeze and will kill you if you drink it…so please don’t do that! </p><br><p>Our formulations use polyethylene glycol that is both non-absorbable and very low dose, meaning that it does not get absorbed into your body and it will not cause GI distress or any of those other symptoms/issues that you may have heard about.<br>For more information, please see <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer" href="https://troscriptions.com/blogs/main/polyethylene-glycol-peg"><u>this article</u></a> for an in-depth explanation.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="a6335a97-5786-45ea-8b12-dd238721e47a" class="r-26sr1i"></div><div data-rid="34bab60f-9d83-41e7-a461-18f0a9886826" class="r-12l1kqk" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="da768285-3fee-467b-9798-7f4c010d7fd1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rbmr2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-7hoa0w"><div data-rid="06e1b752-cfb0-479e-9c95-94457233d41e" class="r-unup99 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How many troches am I getting?</p></span></div><div data-rid="2766622a-c122-476e-991a-da6f247bbe35" class="r-ocpnp4" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-ykev97" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rbmr2:"><div data-rid="cb6f6718-d29a-4004-954f-e373f865b9c0" class="r-2rks0"><div data-rid="8e2ef108-14eb-44e2-9e7a-c79020fefea0" class="r-h34637 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>There are 4 whole troches in each package and each troche can be cut into four quarters. Therefore, one pack can yield up to 16 doses, depending on your personalized needs. The troches are scored for easy titration.</p><p> </p><p>Start with 1/4 troche to 1/2 troche and increase the dosage until you reach your optimal dose.</p><p>DO NOT exceed more than 4 whole troches in a 24-hour period. </p><br><p>For Tro+ Blue, the above instructions may not apply. Please follow the directions from your healthcare provider.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="8be96735-f54a-4e93-b608-44e1e87d2c2a" class="r-1l05xvs"></div><div data-rid="4634eacd-e